{
  "texts": [
    "The set of features from the eGeMAPS are oriented to provide a simplified and standardized selection of relevant acoustic parameters for detecting physiological changes in voice production guided by findings of previous related studies [15].",
    "Based on prior research [19,20], we adopted the default configuration provided by the OpenSMILE library [15,46].",
    "The variables were calculated from the eighteen low level descriptors using a symmetric moving average filter of three frames long.",
    "For a more comprehensive understanding of the computation of the paralinguistic variables, readers are directed to [15].",
    "In total 176 variables were extracted from the voice recordings."
  ]
}